WEBVTT


00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:01.640
The court considers that

00:00:01.640 --> 00:00:03.900
with regard to the present situation,

00:00:03.920 --> 00:00:04.880
Israel must,

00:00:04.880 --> 00:00:07.880
in accordance with its obligations under the Genocide

00:00:07.880 --> 00:00:11.940
Convention in relation to Palestinians in Gaza,

00:00:12.120 --> 00:00:14.360
take all measures within its power

00:00:14.360 --> 00:00:16.800
to prevent the commission of all acts

00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:19.680
within the scope of article 2 of the convention,

00:00:19.680 --> 00:00:20.820
in particular

00:00:21.040 --> 00:00:22.860
a killing groups

00:00:22.880 --> 00:00:24.120
members of the group,

00:00:24.120 --> 00:00:26.120
b causing serious

00:00:26.120 --> 00:00:28.780
bodily or mental harm to members of the group

00:00:29.120 --> 00:00:32.120
C deliberately inflicting on the group

00:00:32.120 --> 00:00:34.760
conditions of life calculated to bring about

00:00:34.760 --> 00:00:37.460
its physical destruction in the holaryn part

00:00:37.480 --> 00:00:40.220
and d imposing measures

00:00:40.520 --> 00:00:43.000
intended to prevent bursts within the group.
